  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A bright, hopeful lead voice at the high register — starts clear and singing. JOURNEY at 0.4 puts it in a recognizable place: a synth lead. As aftertouch rises, the Voyager Drift deepens, the shimmer climbs, and at 0.7 the patch blooms into something luminous and strange over 2 seconds. This is the neuron firing: impulse, transmission, new state.",
